description:
Chobani Plain 05 Fat Greek Yogurt Perfectly crafted using wholesome Australian milk with the addition of live cultures Delicious alone or as a blank canvas to any cooking creation it is so deliciously thick creamy and packed with protein

With over 16 grams of natural protein in every serve this is a great versatile lowfat greek yogurt that can be used as a healthy ingredient in cooking as a topping or served with fruit This Plain Greek Yogurt is perfect for adding to smoothies to create a thick and creamy beverage high in natural protein

At Chobani we believe yogurt should be simple just milk and cultures which we strain using a centuriesold authentic process to make it deliciously thick It takes 3 cups of milk to make 1 cup of Chobani Yogurt which is why its so creamy and packed with protein

No preservatives artificial colours or flavours

High in natural protein?
name: Chobani Plain 0.5% Fat Greek Yogurt Yoghurt 907g
